^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A few things to discuss here. First of all, let's count Lisa's Bergen points once Roberta opens 1S. She has 12 starting points--10 HCP, 1 length point, 1 quality suit point, and -1 dubious singleton HJ. After Roberta opens 1S Lisa can add 3 points for the singleton with 4 trumps. That gives her 15, which is a game forcing hand. Jacoby 2N is not available by a passed hand. However, Lisa has a very nice bid available, which is a 4H splinter bid. Now, let us find out whether and how can Roberta make 12 tricks.|
