^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Well, with 2+ card support, it is almost always better to play in a major suit. And with a singleton or void in partner's suit, NT will be difficult unless you have your own source of tricks. So, never try to "rescue" partner if you have a singleton or void in their suit.|
